{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1c462007d1","title":"漫谈“三K党”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4579afde10","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"1c462007d1"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"25804569a0","name":"蒋兴仁"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c6812b799a","type":"title","text":"漫谈“三K党”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c462007d1"},{"id":"5bcec3c722","type":"authors","text":"北京大学蒋兴仁","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c462007d1"},{"id":"887385e750","type":"paragraph","text":"“三K党”是反动政权下的一个反动组织，我也不了解他的底细，据说他们一贯在青年中进行暗探工作，将进步的青年向反动政府告密，他们还到处听消息，钉稍在青年中制造一种不团结的空气。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c462007d1"},{"id":"0fda6c3875","type":"paragraph","text":"目前我校不团结的现象日益增长，这是什么原因，我们必须追根查底：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c462007d1"},{"id":"a1afdf2e9a","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的条件没有组织调查同学谁是反革命类似于三K党的秘密工作组不用怀疑。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c462007d1"},{"id":"66954d31ee","type":"paragraph","text":"反革命用正面人物和反面人物的身分来挑拨离间，我也是没有的。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c462007d1"},{"id":"07efe8104d","type":"paragraph","text":"问题在于我们有一些同学不信任同学和反社会主义活动已经掀起了的错误思想下，在向国民党学习，在向“三K党”学习，而且个别干部和领导同志主动的带头我想也不足是绝对没有的。清醒一点吧！这又何必。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c462007d1"},{"id":"fb862323c9","type":"paragraph","text":"清醒一点吧！你自己会知道怎样才是利于敌人怎样才是利于自己。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c462007d1"},{"id":"5f4d982b23","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c462007d1"}],"page":{"id":"79ba1b33a1","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1c462007d1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}